      <context>
         <p>Follow this procedure to zero the melter pressure transmitters:</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <note id="note_fqm_2qx_5cc">
               <table id="table_uv5_2qx_5cc">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>PPE Required: Cotton forming gloves.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Caution: Hot surfaces.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </note>
            <p>Go to the melter pressure transmitter.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Close the process valve.</li>
                  <li>Open the equalizing valve.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_lgn_jqx_5cc">
                     <image href="media/image2.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            align="center"
                            scale="50"
                            id="image_mgn_jqx_5cc"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <note>
               <table id="table_ykr_gqx_5cc">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>PPE Required: Cotton forming gloves.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Caution: Hot surfaces.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </note>
            <p>If the reading is 0 kPa (0 in H₂O):</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Close the equalizing valve.</li>
                  <li>Open the process valve.</li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>If the reading is not 0 kPa (0 in H₂O):</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Verify that the process valve is closed.</li>
                  <li>Verify that the equalizing valve is open.</li>
                  <li>Zero the pressure transmitter.</li>
               </ul>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <note>
               <table id="table_grb_hqx_5cc">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>PPE Required: Cotton forming gloves.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Caution: Hot surfaces.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </note>
            <p>Remove the cap from the front of the pressure transmitter.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Press <uicontrol>E</uicontrol> to enter the main menu.</li>
                  <li>Press <uicontrol>+</uicontrol> until Quick Setup is displayed.</li>
                  <li>Press <uicontrol>E</uicontrol> to enter the Position Zero Adjust
                     menu.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_dmx_4qx_5cc">
                     <image href="media/image3.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            align="center"
                            scale="50"
                            id="image_emx_4qx_5cc"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <note>
               <table id="table_n5q_hqx_5cc">
                  <tgroup cols="2">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1*"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>PPE Required: Cotton forming gloves.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                           <entry/>
                           <entry>
                              <p>Caution: Hot surfaces.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </note>
            <p>Perform a Position Zero Adjust using the <uicontrol>–</uicontrol>,
                  <uicontrol>+</uicontrol>, and <uicontrol>E</uicontrol> buttons.</p>
            <p>
               <ul>
                  <li>Verify that the measured value goes to 0 mm H₂O (0 in H₂O).</li>
                  <li>Press the <uicontrol>–</uicontrol> and <uicontrol>+</uicontrol> buttons
                     simultaneously twice to return to the main screen.</li>
                  <li>Close the equalizing valve.</li>
                  <li>Open the process valve.</li>
               </ul>
               <p>
                  <fig id="fig_c1c_wqx_5cc">
                     <image href="media/image4.jpg"
                            placement="break"
                            align="center"
                            scale="50"
                            id="image_d1c_wqx_5cc"/>
                  </fig>
               </p>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
